OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be dry with
OL,6,Fvariable cloud cover. Some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells developing by this
OL,8,Fafternoon. Feeling pleasantly warm in
OL,9,Fany afternoon sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry.
OL,12,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,13,Fdry across all parts with variable
OL,14,Famounts of cloud and clear periods.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FAfter a dry morning rain
OL,17,Fwill spread southeast during the
OL,18,Fafternoon. Mild in the morning but
OL,19,Fturning colder during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
